{"tw": {"2971750": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "雙面夜孃", "steam_appid": 2971750, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.poster.avif?t=1762871174\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.webm?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.mp4?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲概述   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《雙面夜孃》是一款以夜總會文化為背景的視覺小說。玩家將以女主角亞妃的視角出發，體驗夜總會第一紅牌的人生經歷，與債主（同時也是夜總會老闆）的愛恨糾葛。亞妃晚上是指名率最高，業績強強滾的超級紅牌，白天在家則是一個足不出戶的宅女。為了家里的債務考量，她不得不做自己不想做的事，而你也將見證著亞妃的無奈並對此感同身受...... <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/6c6d20a5924eec1a536a4dffe1363268.avif?t=1762871174\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介紹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亞妃，24歲，因為家里債務的關係被迫下海，成為夜總會銀孃的紅牌兼媽媽桑。憑藉天然呆與讓人戀愛的氣場，能擄獲任何酒客的芳心，業績永遠的第一名。被老闆兼自己的主人發現抖M的一面後，每日承受慣老闆的業績壓力，沒達到就會被打屁股懲罰。達到了，則會獎勵愛的棒棒......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/86c4d82cc76d8db3c9824305222de02b.avif?t=1762871174\" width=400 height=599 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >私底下是一個不修邊幅的宅女，在遊戲中你將能見識到紅牌夜孃私底下不為人知的那一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/d100961e6cf18d1010c7ef4efcd6483d.avif?t=1762871174\" width=400 height=599 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有趣的卡牌遊戲，選擇對應效果、組建牌組，爭取更多業績。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >台式鄉土劇設定，讓你置身八點檔，體驗夜晚人生！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中、日、台配音，你一定沒想過可以體驗獨一無二的台語色色！！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/3dec49d7db40bf500adf966cf38735af.avif?t=1762871174\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.poster.avif?t=1762871174\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.webm?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e79