s/steam/apps/2971750/extras/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>", "short_description": "亞妃，24歲，高級夜總會銀孃的紅牌兼媽媽桑。光鮮亮麗的她，在燈紅酒綠的背後，只是一個不喜社交的內向宅女。深入人心的視覺小說，帶你一同探究都市叢林中的愛慾情仇！", "supported_languages": "繁體中文<strong>*</strong>, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/454197493cd0c28a99ff9399174680a384ac39c6/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1762871174", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/5129982f37e3c267521163321dcaca770720d25c/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1762871174", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/5129982f37e3c267521163321dcaca770720d25c/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1762871174", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10+<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel® Core™ i5 10th gen or above<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> GeForce® GTX 960 4GB or above<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong>  Windows Compatible Audio Device<br></li><li><strong>備註:</strong> dGPU recommended</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["樹懶叫工作室", "Maker製造機"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "LewdLoco", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18700, "final": 16800, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 187", "final_formatted": "NT$ 168"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 68, "description": "自訂音量控制"}, {"id": 74, "description": "遊玩無需快速反應"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}, {"id": "2", "description": "策略"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 10 月 23 日"}}}}, "us": {"2971750": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Homebody Hostess", "steam_appid": 2971750, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.poster.avif?t=1762871174\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.webm?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.mp4?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Homebody Hostess </i>is a visual novel set within the backdrop of nightclub culture. Play as the female protagonist Aki and experience life as a nightclub's hotshot hostess, and her love-hate relationship with a debtor (who happens to be her boss). She's the most requested hostess at the nightclub and is also its highest earner. However, when she's off work and being her real self, she's just an introverted homebody. In order to deal with her family's debt, she's forced to do some things she'd rather not. You'll be there to witness and empathize with Aki and her struggles...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/6c6d20a5924eec1a536a4dffe1363268.avif?t=1762871174\" width=600 height=338 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aki is 24 years old, and to deal with her family's debt, she's been forced to work as a nightclub hostess and madam. All the customers are easily smitten with Aki's natural aloofness and loving aura, so it's no surprise she's always the nightclub's top earner. After her debtor/boss discovers her masochistic tendencies, he starts putting incredible pressure on her to make more. If she doesn't reach her target, she gets a spanking for being a naughty girl. But if she does, he gives her that yummy, sweet candy stick...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/86c4d82cc76d8db3c9824305222de02b.avif?t=1762871174\" width=400 height=599 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alas! Aki's actually just an introverted homebody who doesn't care that much about her appearance. Throughout the game, you'll learn that some hot hostesses aren't actually all about that dazzling nightlife.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/d100961e6cf18d1010c7ef4efcd6483d.avif?t=1762871174\" width=400 height=599 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging card game—choose effects, build your deck, and fight for better sales performance!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the world of Taiwanese soap operas, with over-the-top drama and traditional local flair, you'll feel like you're living in a primetime melodrama!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voiced in Mandarin, Japanese, and Taiwanese Hokkien—you never imagined erotic scenes could sound <i>this</i> uniquely Taiwanese!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/3dec49d7db40bf500adf966cf38735af.avif?t=1762871174\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.poster.avif?t=1762871174\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.webm?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/393c68e796812de84d6b7c7cc8a5002a.mp4?t=1762871174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Homebody Hostess </i>is a visual novel set within the backdrop of nightclub culture. Play as the female protagonist Aki and experience life as a nightclub's hotshot hostess, and her love-hate relationship with a debtor (who happens to be her boss). She's the most requested hostess at the nightclub and is also its highest earner. However, when she's off work and being her real self, she's just an introverted homebody. In order to deal with her family's debt, she's forced to do some things she'd rather not. You'll be there to witness and empathize with Aki and her struggles...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/6c6d20a5924eec1a536a4dffe1363268.avif?t=1762871174\" width=600 height=338 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aki is 24 years old, and to deal with her family's debt, she's been forced to work as a nightclub hostess and madam. All the customers are easily smitten with Aki's natural aloofness and loving aura, so it's no surprise she's always the nightclub's top earner. After her debtor/boss discovers her masochistic tendencies, he starts putting incredible pressure on her to make more. If she doesn't reach her target, she gets a spanking for being a naughty girl. But if she does, he gives her that yummy, sweet candy stick...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/86c4d82cc76d8db3c9824305222de02b.avif?t=1762871174\" width=400 height=599 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alas! Aki's actually just an introverted homebody who doesn't care that much about her appearance. Throughout the game, you'll learn that some hot hostesses aren't actually all about that dazzling nightlife.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/d100961e6cf18d1010c7ef4efcd6483d.avif?t=1762871174\" width=400 height=599 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging card game—choose effects, build your deck, and fight for better sales performance!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the world of Taiwanese soap operas, with over-the-top drama and traditional local flair, you'll feel like you're living in a primetime melodrama!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voiced in Mandarin, Japanese, and Taiwanese Hokkien—you never imagined erotic scenes could sound <i>this</i> uniquely Taiwanese!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/3dec49d7db40bf500adf966cf38735af.avif?t=1762871174\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/ef47d1f839b12b6390c5f905b9996bb7.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/extras_big/8e38d5f869a928afd4d81d903e3f2a91.avif?t=1762871174 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>", "short_description": "Aki is 24 years old, working as the madam and hottest hostess at a fancy nightclub. Beneath the glamorous facade she puts on at night, she's actually an introverted homebody. This heartwarming visual novel explores love, desire, and the dog-eat-dog world of the urban jungle!", "supported_languages": "Traditional Chinese<strong>*</strong>, English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Simplified Chinese<strong>*</strong>, Korean<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/7a8975004b63f79eb8c85b636ee6f65fa982d64b/header.jpg?t=1762871174", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/e94c68d7869397a58b90adb3e31ec15e47e6b3cd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1762871174", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971750/e94c68d7869397a58b90adb3e31ec15e47e6b3cd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1762871174", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel® Core™ i5 10th gen or above<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GeForce® GTX 960 4GB or above<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 4 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong>  Windows Compatible Audio Device<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> dGPU recommended</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["樹懶叫工作室", "Maker製造機"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "LewdLoco", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "USD", "initial": 899, "final": 809, "discount_percent": 10